The root directory contains all other directories in the system and it is represented with a "/" but the home directory is a personal directory inside the root directory where files are stored.
The git pull command to used to update changes in the local repository from the remote repository.
Git pull is used before starting a new work or making changes to an already existing one making sure that the userr is working on the most current version of the codebase.
And when collaborating with others, git pull is used to avoid conflicts.
